      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh fine but if I really can't go today, what's the absolute safest way to do it at home? like if I use a warm soak and a heavy layer of antibiotic ointment, would that be enough to stop it from getting worse until I can go later this week? i just want to know what the standard procedure is for minor stuff like this.",
